    Returns the footprint for a GEO product

    footprint.Rd

    GEO products do not have an individual footprint. Instead, this resource represents a GEO footprint for the respective sensor mode and sub satellite longitude.

    Usage

    footprint(
  sensorMode,
  subSatelliteLongitude,
  returnPolygon = TRUE,
  plotPolygon = FALSE
)

    Arguments

    sensorMode

    Sensor Mode; one of: ALTHRV, REDSCN, NOMSCN

    subSatelliteLongitude

    Sub Satellite longitude in degrees

    returnPolygon

    TRUE if a polygon should be returned; FALSE to return the response

    plotPolygon

    if the polygon is to be plotted

    Value

    If returnPolygon is TRUE then a sf polygon else the response as an R list
